---
title: Lamb Ragu Pappardelle with Roasted Red Pepper
description: Here at HelloFresh we're all about bringing variety to dinnertime and helping you to climb out of culinary ruts. It's so easy to get stuck in habits. Like automatically reaching for the beef mince when making a pasta sauce. Why not ring the changes and try lamb instead? In tonight's dinner it makes a richly flavoured ragu for wide ribbons of pappardelle. Enjoy!
